data.description: Beautiful home in Chandler's Griffin Estates. This home features a large, open concept living, dining and kitchen area. Split bedroom layout allows for privacy. Half of the garage has been enclosed and is currently used for a nice home office and play room for the kids. The other half of the garage still serves as good storage. Fenced back yard is great for pets and the family. New AC unit in 2021.
